							h3 About 
							p Worn and Faded is a documentary celebrating the history, evolution, design, and social relevance of the Rock Tee.
					.col-lg-7
						.animatable(data-animate="animate__animated animate__fadeInUp")
							h3 Why It Matters
							p From an ignored piece of merchandise in the late 1960s to a thriving multi-million dollar business in the 1980s, the story of the band shirt involves visionary entrepreneurs, cutting edge graphic designers, musicians and fans across the world.

							p In the process, it evolves from an article of clothing to an integral tool in the expression of self-identity to millions of young people. Pioneers such as Dell Furano have recently passed away so it’s more important than ever to get others’ stories while we can. 
