						p Director and Editor Benjamin Jones has been creating video content professionally since 2006. He has worked extensively in the printed apparel space and has produced videos for Motion Textile, Jak Prints, the Ink Kitchen, Print Hustlers Conference, Made Lab and Bella + Canvas. Music is a strong passion of his and he has produced over 50 music videos through his production company TBJ Productions and has worked with artists such as DEVO, Cold War Kids, Marilyn Manson, Zakk Wylde, Andrew W.K. and many more. www.tbjproductions.com
